ARABIA; RELIGION -- SAUDI ARABIA; DEMONSTRATIONS -- SAUDI ARABIA; IRAQ -- 
FOREIGN RELATIONS -- KUWAIT; IRAQ -- ARMED FORCES -- KUWAIT; MILITARY 
CONFRONTATIONS; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES -- SAUDI ARABIA 
</P>
