<TEXT>
<P>
Dangerfield Sued Over Dog Story: Comedy actor-writer Harold Ramis sued comedian 
Rodney Dangerfield, accusing him of stealing an idea for a film about a dog 
named Rover Dangerfield "who looked and acted like Dangerfield." In the federal 
court suit seeking at least $1 million, Ramis claims that he conceived of Rover 
Dangerfield in 1986 and told Dangerfield about his idea of making a movie about 
the dog. 
</P>
